          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Cross-section measured using activation method",
                "for flux monitor.",
                "The principle of this method is to determine the",
                "neutron flux strength by the radioactivity of the",
                "reaction product 7Be in the LiF target. In this case,",
                "it is of special advantage, that the y-ray energies",
                "occurring in the decays of 7Be and l98Au are very",
                "similar and therefore the ratio of the",
                "gamma-efficiencies of the used NaI(Tl) detector is",
                "near to one."
              ]
            }
          ],
